@cmack102 Hey Chad,

Give us a call at 625-7200 (Trinidad &amp; Tobago Local Calls) or 1-800-523-5585 (International Calls) and one of our agents will happily assist you with your booking!

-Alvin

@mspertab Hi there,

We've noted you submitted a claim for Damaged Baggage and wish to assist.  Please send us a private message with the unique claim number you received.

-Alvin

@deearrjaybee Hi there, thank you for sharing this with us. We'll have our team look into this problem.

In the meantime we suggest selecting different dates as daily service is not operated to some destinations.

-Alvin

@_lifeinreverse Hey there, student discount is applicable for Economy-Flex to Biz-Flex fares. These fares include checked baggage, more miles and are refundable. 
Hope this offers some clarification. 

- Kezia
